name: Long Johnson
description: "Olong Johnson" is a humorous phrase originating from a viral video featuring a talking cat. In the video, the cat is vocalizing a phrase that sounds just like "Olong Johnson". The amount of popularity Olong Johnson video has gained, due to the cat's seemingly human-like utterance. During this time the video has been widely shared and referenced in various memes and remixes. One of the biggest and most famous references of this video is from the comedy show South Park.
